      "datePublished": "1994-01",
      "articleBody": "In 1994-5 I started playing SimCity 2000 and Transport Tycoon. I became interested in studying Geography and I was continuously browsing atlases. I was already designing many maps, but I did not yet have the right tools to help me analyse the data behind them. Now that I have closed that gap, I can implement my abilities in favour of the resources of our planet.",
